20,1,$1+$1,$4,$5,$6,$7,0*
20,1,$1+$1,$6,$7,$8,$9,0*
20,1,$1+$1,$8,$9,$2,$3,0*%
%AMOutline5P*
0 Free polygon, 5 corners , with rotation*
0 The origin of the aperture is its center*
0 number of corners: always 5*
